{"tid":526736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"俄羅斯奇招鼓勵後生仔投票：票站外自拍即有機會獲贈iPhone","createTime":"2018-01-12T02:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T03:04:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"279ae772f59eb30f3deba1cfcaca13109d6f670a","tid":526736,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:09:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180112/bknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180112%2Fbknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001.html&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5fQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=f2370815\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180112/bknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯將於3月舉行總統選舉，雖然有分析認為現任總統普京勢將篤定連任，但克里姆林宮仍希望推高投票率，讓普京可以手執「高民望」當選。有俄羅斯傳媒報道，政府為鼓勵年青一輩投票，決定舉行「投票自拍送iPhone」的活動。年青人只要在投票後，站在票站前自拍，即有機會贏得iPhone等蘋果公司電子產品。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180112/photo/bknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180112052429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180112%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180112052429&h=0af611a9&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"fdce0384bc9d54e54db66587fa193a7050e425fb","tid":526736,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬唔係禁iphone?"},{"pid":"f21a90135b4697a59a67bd3a2792ad5fc7af0499","tid":526736,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdce0384bc9d54e54db66587fa193a7050e425fb","tid":526736,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:13:25.000Z","msg":"俄佬唔係禁iphone?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:13:52.000Z","msg":"所以先有效"},{"pid":"0cb79ebb00c7671c07517af526d2af179eaf87b0","tid":526736,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"如果投建制有iPhoneX/8，有幾多後生會投？"},{"pid":"3e74f7aeef9ad93a510d390995f6472855689e31","tid":526736,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"報道指，政府的目標是要將投票率推高至7成，當中18至39歲的界別為重點，目前已聘用了兩間公關公司籌備活動。按照計劃，所有參加者必須先投票後再自拍，當中最優秀的照片便可獲獎。政府在去年9月的7個地方選舉中，已率先推行相關活動，當時政府以iPhone 7、iPad及Apple Watch作為獎品。 <br />\n<br />\n政治分析員（Alexei Makarkin）認為，政府希望透過這類活動，在鼓勵年青年投票同時，這批青年亦會帶同家中的長輩前往投票，甚至將其打造成為潮流，從而推動更多人投票。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180112/photo/bknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001_02p.jpg?20180112052429\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180112%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180112020002951-0112_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180112052429&h=52e8b881&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b1387829c91ff138fa0213b83f521dc88dc71f7c","tid":526736,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb79ebb00c7671c07517af526d2af179eaf87b0","tid":526736,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:15:55.000Z","msg":"如果投建制有iPhoneX/8，有幾多後生會投？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"犯法"},{"pid":"66d5f39ce7de154ec2a08bc7417ca82030b0a460","tid":526736,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T03:04:24.000Z","msg":"普京訓係到都贏架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲搞咁多野"}]}